        "created_at": "2022-09-16T00:06:24.291Z",
        "cooked": "<p>This should be easy, though it probably depends on the FDB version (we changed OpenSSL stuff multiple times). The easiest way would be to remove <a href=\"https://github.com/apple/foundationdb/blob/e9a12b4a1a0c8941eb15a6677cdd59e7a99ad8b3/cmake/FDBComponents.cmake#L38\">this line</a> (default for cmake is linking against the dynamic library)</p>",
